dtpsLMS.html.title: dtpsLMS
dtpsLMS.html.name: dtpsLMS
dtpsLMS.html.description: Global DTPS LMS integration object. All LMS-related tasks, such as fetching data, are handled by this object. This is always loaded first.

dtpsLMS.html#.commonHeaders.title: <static> commonHeaders
dtpsLMS.html#.commonHeaders.name: commonHeaders
dtpsLMS.html#.commonHeaders.description: Common headers used for Canvas web requests. This variable is specific to Canvas LMS integration in DTPS and is not required for other LMS integrations.

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchUser.title: <static> fetchUser()  {Promise.<User>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchUser.name: fetchUser
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchUser.description: [REQUIRED] Fetches user data from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchClasses.title: <static> fetchClasses()  {Promise.<Array.<Class>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchClasses.name: fetchClasses
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchClasses.description: [REQUIRED] Fetches class data from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchAssignments.title: <static> fetchAssignments( classID )  {Promise.<Array.<Assignment>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchAssignments.name: fetchAssignments
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchAssignments.description: [REQUIRED] Fetches assignment data for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchModules.title: <static> fetchModules( classID )  {Promise.<Array.<Module>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchModules.name: fetchModules
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchModules.description: [OPTIONAL] Fetches module data for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.collapseModule.title: <static> collapseModule( classID, moduleID, collapsed )  {Promise}
dtpsLMS.html#.collapseModule.name: collapseModule
dtpsLMS.html#.collapseModule.description: [OPTIONAL] Collapses a module in the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchAnnouncements.title: <static> fetchAnnouncements( classID )  {Promise.<Array.<Announcement>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchAnnouncements.name: fetchAnnouncements
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchAnnouncements.description: [OPTIONAL] Fetches recent announcements for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchHomepage.title: <static> fetchHomepage( classID )  {Promise.<string>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchHomepage.name: fetchHomepage
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchHomepage.description: [OPTIONAL] Fetches homepage HTML for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchUsers.title: <static> fetchUsers( classID )  {Promise.<Array.<ClassSection>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchUsers.name: fetchUsers
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchUsers.description: [OPTIONAL] Fetches the users for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchDiscussionThreads.title: <static> fetchDiscussionThreads( classID )  {Promise.<Array.<PartialDiscussionThread>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchDiscussionThreads.name: fetchDiscussionThreads
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchDiscussionThreads.description: [OPTIONAL] Fetches discussion threads for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchDiscussionPosts.title: <static> fetchDiscussionPosts( classID, threadID )  {Promise.<DiscussionThread>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchDiscussionPosts.name: fetchDiscussionPosts
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchDiscussionPosts.description: [REQUIRED IF dtpsLMS.fetchDiscussionThreads IS IMPLEMENTED] Fetches discussion posts in a thread from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchPages.title: <static> fetchPages( classID )  {Promise.<Array.<PartialPage>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchPages.name: fetchPages
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchPages.description: [OPTIONAL] Fetches pages for a course from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.fetchPageContent.title: <static> fetchPageContent( classID, pageID )  {Promise.<Page>}
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchPageContent.name: fetchPageContent
dtpsLMS.html#.fetchPageContent.description: [REQUIRED IF dtpsLMS.fetchPages IS IMPLEMENTED] Fetches content for a page from the LMS

dtpsLMS.html#.gradebook.title: <static> gradebook( course )  {Promise.<string>}
dtpsLMS.html#.gradebook.name: gradebook
dtpsLMS.html#.gradebook.description: [OPTIONAL] Renders custom gradebook HTML for unique grading systems or for a more tailored experience. The gradebook only shows for classes with a grade and with at least 1 assignment.

dtpsLMS.html#.gradebookDidRender.title: <static> gradebookDidRender( course )
dtpsLMS.html#.gradebookDidRender.name: gradebookDidRender
dtpsLMS.html#.gradebookDidRender.description: [OPTIONAL] Called after the HTML returned by dtpsLMS.gradebook has rendered. Runs any initialization needed for the gradebook, such as enabling interactive elements or what-if grades.

dtpsLMS.html#.calculateGrade.title: <static> calculateGrade( course, assignments )  {undefined|object}
dtpsLMS.html#.calculateGrade.name: calculateGrade
dtpsLMS.html#.calculateGrade.description: [OPTIONAL] Calculates class grades with a custom grade calculation formula. Used for unique grading systems.

dtpsLMS.html#.updateAssignments.title: <static> updateAssignments( assignments )  {Promise.<Array.<Assignment>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.updateAssignments.name: updateAssignments
dtpsLMS.html#.updateAssignments.description: [OPTIONAL, INSTITUTION ONLY] This function can be implemented by institution-specific scripts to loop through and override assignment data returned by the LMS.

dtpsLMS.html#.updateClasses.title: <static> updateClasses( classes )  {Promise.<Array.<Class>>}
dtpsLMS.html#.updateClasses.name: updateClasses
dtpsLMS.html#.updateClasses.description: [OPTIONAL, INSTITUTION ONLY] This function can be implemented by institution-specific scripts to loop through and override class data returned by the LMS.
